posting_body: ['Summer Vibes', 'La Vina Apartments in Livermore, CA', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 56', 'OR Text', '56', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'La Vina', '4601 Gerrilyn Way , Livermore, CA, 94550', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 887 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'La Vina offers a wonderful combination of modern living and the serene natural beauty of the Livermore Valley.', 'Central air conditioning and full-sized washers and dryers make living comfortable and convenient at our Livermore apartments.', 'Our units also feature dishwashers and balconies or patios.', 'When it comes to community amenities, our apartments in Livermore offer a sparkling pool, assigned covered parking, a fitness center and more.', 'La Vina is just minutes from supermarkets, banks, family restaurants, good neighborhood schools, parks and golf courses.', "If you're searching for apartments in Livermore, look no further.", "You'll love coming home to the beautifully landscaped community of La Vina.", 'AMC-CA, Inc.dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE # 01525033', 'Features', '- Cable Ready', '- Walk in Closets', '- Balcony / Patio', '- Ceiling Fans Select Units', '- Central Heat and Air', '- Furnished Available', '- Pets Welcome', '- Washer/Dryers', '- Vaulted Ceilings', '- Dishwasher', 'Community Amenities', '- Assigned Parking', '- Cable or Satellite', '- Broadband Internet Access', '- Club House', '- Pool', '- Short Term Lease', '- Wireless Internet Access', '- Playground Fortress', '- Convenient Location', 'Pet Policy', 'Dogs & Cats are welcomed, Breed Restrictions apply.', 'Pet Cleaning & Damages Deposit will be required and Monthly Pet Rent.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'sd67LFIO17']
